# W4 calibration outputs — confidential per ADR-0009 Amendment 1 §G.
# Local-only runs under scripts/calibration/; real data stays off-Git.
w4_calibration*.json
w4_manifest.json

# Generic calibration-harness private payloads (ADR-0020 §"Publication-scope").
# The harness emits ``<protocol_name>_private.json`` containing per-observation
# detail (program-key hashes + label + confidence + rules_fired). NEVER commit;
# operator archives to ``meridianiq-private/calibration/<cycle>-<wave>/``.
*_private.json
